channel.title: Alternative for the 'process' method
channel.description:
Usually instead of using process I use the walking/clicking packets to update things, but it would not work in this case.
See, I'm trying to make skulls stay on until the 30-minute timer runs out, but I'm forced to use process. Is there an alternative for this?
